column5: A friend has asked if I can look at his HDS Live. Wondering if anyone knows where I can get schematics ? Looks like the first transformer on the power circuit but I need a part number. Thanks.
Just need a pic or part number. It is the common mode choke (L49). Thanks
Tech at Lowrance said the part number doesn't show in their system and wondered what schematic I was looking for.
E Mail the pic. I am sure that would be the quickest way to confirm .
They may not be too eager to give out that info? It works better for them if you throw it out and buy a new one?
